- For using the saved model to eval
python3 ./main.py --eval --load_model --path="./" --test_file="test.json" 

- For training the model using default hyperparameters
python3 ./main.py --train

- For training the model using assigned hyperparameters
python3 ./main.py --train --batch=128 --epochs=1 --learning_rate=0.0002 

- For training with pretrained model using default hyperparameters
python3 ./main.py --load_model --train